ca.ualberta.cs.cmput301w15t04team04project

Class FragmentEditClaim1

  • java.lang.Object
    • ca.ualberta.cs.cmput301w15t04team04project.FragmentEditClaim1

  • public class FragmentEditClaim1
extends java.lang.Object
    This is the fragment part 1 for adding/editing a claim.
    1. In this part, you need to fill out the information shown on the scream.
      • Enter the claim name (String).
      • Select the start date of the claim (DatePicker).
      • Select the end date of the claim (DatePicker).
      • Enter the description of the claim (String).
    Since:
    2015-03-10, 2015-03-15
    Version:
    1.0, 1.1
    Author:
    Ji Yang, Yang Zhang, Yufei Zhang
